messages.message: Hey team! I just merged in a backend PR, and I need to redeploy the webapp in crafting-cyp for a couple of Cypress tests to pass in Cypress CI. I'll update once redeployment has completed.

<!subteam^S02FJA6A7U5> (low priority)
Looks like the pipeline is taking way too long? It stuck at "*Verify All Deployments*" step (42 mins and continuing)
https://jenkins.instabase.com/job/SAAS-AWS/job/saas-pipelines/job/install-ib-platform/

Not sure if this is the reason, but the "observability-agent" of this webapp pod failed to start.
https://crafting-cyp.test.instabase.com/deployment-manager/dashboard/deployments/apps/v1/webapp/deployment-webapp-757fb8b894-zqtc8

Well, the update failed, but Cypress CI should continue to work (i hope...). These 2 Cypress tests are expected to fail until the next successful webapp deployment:
• `apps/src/aihub/__e2e__/Landing/sign-up.spec.ts`
• `apps/src/aihub/__e2e__/Settings/Account/edit-account.spec.ts`
